{"tid":2038361,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"鍾意咗個啤酒妹","createTime":"2020-05-27T13:39:41.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-28T22:26:25.000Z","uid":281240,"like":24,"dislike":69,"uniUserReply":58,"replies":[{"pid":"0a6cc2454dcf453f9d93b8b1f58b02af85b9b812","tid":2038361,"uid":281240,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T13:39:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />已經連續兩日特登去嗰間bar為咗見佢<br />\n沉咗船咁<br />\n雖然佢好mk 我平時食開嘅都唔係呢類<br />\n但佢俾到我嗰種好耐都未曾有嘅心動感覺<br />\n諗住傾多晚聽日去抄佢牌<br />\n如果聽日佢會翻嘅話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n希望佢會<br />\n而家喺bar嘅嗰三個鐘就係我每日最開心嘅時候<br />\n佢一收工 我就魂不守舍咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔知第二日會唔會再見到佢<br />\n見到就好開心 見唔到嗰日就會成個人頹撚晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"20cdb4ac4aa6d4baa69487e23833d599cc4c08c8","tid":2038361,"uid":29080,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T13:42:08.000Z","msg":"拎咗電話未"},{"pid":"6b5abc0dbc57f552c450f6893966c27acc9ae415","tid":2038361,"uid":201414,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T13:42:56.000Z","msg":"問佢過夜幾錢"},{"pid":"f944976e144f990ee589e71ab5b8b6b237da1f03","tid":2038361,"uid":281240,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"20cdb4ac4aa6d4baa69487e23833d599cc4c08c8","tid":2038361,"uid":29080,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T13:42:08.000Z","msg":"拎咗電話未"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T13:44:25.000Z","msg":"都話聽日抄 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1828e81aede8475ef18f8d15eaded99f23a6bac","tid":2038361,"uid":281240,"like":5,"dislike":18,"score":-13,"quote":{"pid":"6b5abc0dbc57f552c450f6893966c27acc9ae415","tid":2038361,"uid":201414,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T13:42:56.000Z","msg":"問佢過夜幾錢"},"citedBy":5,"replyTim